r_Droped_Old.gif/120px-Pure_Horror_Droped_Old.gif?8d0364\" width=\"120\" height=\"70\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Beta Dropped Pure Horror Texture.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Resources-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Horror#Resources-0\">Resources</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Craftable_Items-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Horror#Craftable_Items-0\">Craftable Items</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
