  "plainText": "Pure Horror\nObject Info\nPerk\nCan be used as fuel for shadow items\n6 min.\n脳40\nSource\nDropped by\nwith ( only)\nCrafting\nDescription\nTransmute Dreadstone into Pure Horror.\n脳1 ( only)\nAmount produced\n2\nFilters\n(for ).\nMiscellaneous\n\"horrorfuel\"\nExclusive to:\n鈥淚t sends a terrible shiver down my spine.鈥漒n鈥揥ilson\n鈥淭hat must be what nightmares have nightmares about.鈥漒n鈥揥illow\n鈥淪-scary...鈥漒n鈥揥olfgang\n鈥淭here are always more horrors to come.鈥漒n鈥揥endy\n鈥淒ARKNESS: 100%. NO SHADES OF GREY DETECTED鈥漒n鈥揥X-78\n鈥淗ighly concentrated ectoplasmic residue.鈥漒n鈥揥ickerbottom\n鈥淭hat stuff can't be good for ya.鈥漒n鈥揥oodie\n鈥淭hat's the good stuff.鈥漒n鈥揗axwell\n鈥淭he sight 枚f it chills even my c枚urage枚us Viking heart.鈥漒n鈥揥igfrid\n鈥淚t makes our spider skin crawl.鈥漒n鈥揥ebber\n鈥淚t makes my teeth chatter.鈥漒n鈥揥arly\n鈥淪cary...鈥漒n鈥揥ormwood\n鈥淢akes the usual nightmare goop look almost pleasant by comparison.鈥漒n鈥揥inona\n鈥淎 goop most foul.鈥漒n鈥揥ortox\n鈥淚-is just goop! Not scared!鈥漒n鈥揥urt\n鈥淚t can't be THAT bad... can it?鈥漒n鈥揥alter\n鈥淚t gives me a terrible feeling...鈥漒n鈥揥anda\nPure Horror is a resource exclusive to Don't Starve Together. It appears to be a stronger variant of Nightmare Fuel. Before Shadow Rifts are activated, the only sources of Pure Horror are the Nightmare Werepig, which drops 4-5 upon its defeat, and closely examining certain objects with Rose-Colored Glasses as Winona with the Shadow Seeker II skill.\nOnce Shadow Rifts are open, Fused Shadelings are the most efficient way of farming Pure Horror, dropping 3-4 each. Ink Blights drop a smaller amount of Pure Horror as well, but cannot be killed as often. The Resting Horror also drops 1 Pure Horror if Shadow Rifts have been activated.\nPure Horror is used to craft the Dreadstone Helm and Dreadstone Armor, as well as the Shadowcraft Plinth and all of the items craftable at said station in the Shadowcraft Filter. It can also refuel anything fueled by Nightmare Fuel at twice the efficiency. For example, the durability of Bone Armor is restored by 50% per Pure Horror, rather than the usual 25% per Nightmare Fuel.\nWilson with the Shadow Courtier Skill can craft 2 Pure Horror with 1 Dreadstone, as well as use 3 Pure Horror to craft 1 Dreadstone, or use 1 Pure Horror to craft 2 Nightmare Fuel.\nUsage[edit | edit source]\n脳4\n脳6\n脳4\n脳4\n脳2\n脳5\n脳5\n脳3\n脳4\n脳2\n脳5\n脳3\n脳2\n脳5\n脳4\n脳2\n脳8\n脳8\n脳5\n脳4\n脳4\n脳4\n脳2\n脳5\n脳3\n脳2\n脳3\n脳3\n脳2\n脳3\n脳20\nTrivia[edit | edit source]\nThe opposite of this item is Pure Brilliance.\nGallery[edit | edit source]\nDropped Pure Horror.\nBeta Pure Horror Texture.\nBeta Dropped Pure Horror Texture.\nResourcesCraftable Items\nView or edit this template\nResources\nAttention: The following categories are only for the players look up the page based on their first impression, they have nothing to do with the actual categories/behavior/function/tags of these items\nPlants\nNatural non-living materials\nMobs Parts\nSkins\nFeathers\nBones and horns\nGems\nShadow Resources\nLunar Resources\nCraftable Resources\nNon-natural materials\nTrinkets\nLost Relics\nTransmission Items\nView or edit this template\nDon't Starve Together Craftable Items\nRegular Filters\nSurvivor Items\nWilson\nWillow\nWolfgang\nWendy\nWX-78\nWickerbottom\nWoodie\nWes\nMaxwell\nWigfrid\nWebber\nWarly\nWortox\nWormwood\nWinona\nWurt\nWalter\nWanda\nTools\nLight Sources\nPrototypers & Stations\nRefined Materials\nWeapons\nArmor\nClothing\nHealing\nMagic\nDecorations\nStructures\nStorage Solutions\nCooking\nFood & Gardening\nFishing\nSeafaring\nBeefalo Riding\nWinter Items\nSummer Items\nRain Gear\nCrafting Station Filters\nSpecial Event\nAncient Pseudoscience\nCarpentry\nCartography\nCritters\nCelestial\nBrightsmithy\nShadowcraft\nFabrication\nBottle Exchange\nCombrining Filter\nTea Brewing Filter\nSculptures\nSeasonings\nTrading\nTrading Hutch\nOfferings\nCawnival Creation\nTrinket Trove\nMad Science\nWinter's Feast Cooking\nSanctum Smithy Filter\nCustom Course Shack Filter",
