  "title": "Pure Horror",
  "wikitext": "{{Object Infobox\n|burnTime = [[File:Nightmare Fuel.png|32px|link=Fuel/DST#Nightmare Fuel]] 6 min.\n|icon = Pure Horror.png\n|image = Pure Horror Dropped.png\n|craft_desctiption = ''Transmute Dreadstone into Pure Horror.''\n|ingredient1=Dreadstone\n|multiplier1=1 ({{Pic|32|Wilson Portrait|Wilson}} only)\n|filter={{Pic32|Wilson Filter}}\n|numtogive=2\n|perk=Can be used as fuel for shadow items\n|stack=脳40\n|spawnCode=\"horrorfuel\"\n|droppedBy={{Pic32|Nightmare Werepig}}{{Pic24|Resting Horror Planar|Resting Horror}}{{Pic|32|Lurking Nightmare Planar|Lurking Nightmare}}{{Pic24|Fused Shadeling}}{{Pic32|Shriek}}{{Pic32|Rasp}}{{Pic24|Jitters}}{{Pic|32|Rictus}}{{Pic|48|Ornery Chest}}{{Pic32|Void Masque Hat|Void Masque}}{{Pic32|Mega Blight}}\n{{Pic32|Rose-Colored Glasses}} with {{PicDark|32|Shadow Seeker II}} ({{Pic|32|Winona Portrait|Winona}} only)\n|skill = Shadow Courtier\n|skillOwner = Wilson\n}}\n{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve Together}}\n{{Quotes\n|walter=It can't be THAT bad... can it?\n|wilson=It sends a terrible shiver down my spine.\n|wanda=It gives me a terrible feeling...\n|warly=It makes my teeth chatter.\n|wigfrid=The sight 枚f it chills even my c枚urage枚us Viking heart.\n|maxwell=That's the good stuff.\n|webber=It makes our spider skin crawl.\n|wendy=There are always more horrors to come.\n|wickerbottom=Highly concentrated ectoplasmic residue.\n|willow=That must be what nightmares have nightmares about.\n|winona=Makes the usual nightmare goop look almost pleasant by comparison.\n|woodie=That stuff can't be good for ya.\n|wormwood=Scary...\n|wortox=A goop most foul.\n|wurt=I-is just goop! Not scared!\n|wx78=DARKNESS: 100%. NO SHADES OF GREY DETECTED\n|wolfgang=S-scary...\n|choose=willow\n}}\n\n'''Pure Horror''' is a resource exclusive to ''[[Don't Starve Together]]''. It appears to be a stronger variant of [[Nightmare Fuel]]. Before [[Shadow Rift]]s are activated, the only sources of Pure Horror are the [[Nightmare Werepig]], which drops 4-5 upon its defeat, and closely examining certain objects with [[Rose-Colored Glasses]] as [[Winona/Don't Starve Together|Winona]] with the [[Shadow Seeker II]] skill.\n\nOnce Shadow Rifts are open, [[Fused Shadeling]]s are the most efficient way of farming Pure Horror, dropping 3-4 each. [[Ink Blight]]s drop a smaller amount of Pure Horror as well, but cannot be killed as often. The [[Resting Horror]] also drops 1 Pure Horror if Shadow Rifts have been activated.\n\nPure Horror is used to craft the [[Dreadstone Helm]] and [[Dreadstone Armor]], as well as the [[Shadowcraft Plinth]] and all of the items craftable at said station in the [[Shadowcraft Filter]]. It can also refuel anything fueled by Nightmare Fuel at twice the efficiency. For example, the durability of [[Bone Armor]] is restored by 50% per Pure Horror, rather than the usual 25% per Nightmare Fuel.\n\n[[Wilson/Don't Starve Together|Wilson]] with the {{PicDark|24|Shadow Courtier}} ''[[Shadow Courtier]]'' Skill can craft 2 Pure Horror with 1 [[Dreadstone]], as well as use 3 Pure Horror to craft 1 Dreadstone, or use 1 Pure Horror to craft 2 Nightmare Fuel.\n\n== {{Pic32|Icon Tools}} Usage==\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Dreadstone\n|count2 = 6\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|count1 = 4\n|result = Dreadstone Armor\n|tool = Blueprint (rare)\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|count1 = 4\n|item2 = Dreadstone\n|count2 = 4\n|result = Dreadstone Helm\n|tool = Blueprint (rare)}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|item3 = Nightmare Fuel\n|count3 = 5\n|item2 = Dreadstone\n|count2 = 2\n|result = Shadowcraft Plinth Kit\n|tool = Ancient Pseudoscience Station\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|count1 = 5\n|item2 = Dark Tatters DST\n|tool = Shadowcraft Plinth\n|result = Umbralla}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Dark Tatters DST\n|tool = Shadowcraft Plinth\n|result = Shadow Reaper}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|count1 = 4\n|item2 = Dark Tatters DST\n|count2 = 2\n|tool = Shadowcraft Plinth\n|result = Gloomerang}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|count1 = 5\n|item2 = Possessed Shadow Atrium\n|item3 = Dreadstone\n|count3 = 3\n|item4 = Dark Tatters DST\n|count4 = 2\n|tool = Shadowcraft Plinth\n|result = Shadow Maul}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|count1 = 5\n|item2 = Possessed Shadow Atrium\n|item3 = Dreadstone\n|count3 = 4\n|item4 = Dark Tatters DST\n|count4 = 2\n|tool = Shadowcraft Plinth\n|result = Beefalo Gloom Bell}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|count1 = 8\n|item2 = Possessed Shadow Atrium\n|item3 = Dreadstone\n|count3 = 8\n|item4 = Dark Tatters DST\n|count4 = 5\n|tool = Shadowcraft Plinth\n|result = Nightmare Saddle}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|count1 = 4\n|item2 = Dark Tatters DST\n|count2 = 4\n|tool = Shadowcraft Plinth\n|result = Void Robe}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|count1 = 4\n|item2 = Dark Tatters DST\n|count2 = 2\n|tool = Shadowcraft Plinth\n|result = Void Cowl}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|item2 = Dark Tatters DST\n|tool = Shadowcraft Plinth\n|result = Void Repair Kit}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|count1 = 5\n|item2 = Beeswax\n|count2 = 3\n|item3 = Mosquito Sack\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Shadowcraft Plinth\n|result = Embalming Spritz}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item3 = Cut Grass\n|count3 = 3\n|item2 = Boards\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|result = Shadow Boxer\n|tool = Prestihatitator}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|count1 = 3\n|result = Dreadstone\n|resultcount = 1\n|skill = Shadow Courtier\n|character = Wilson\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|result = Nightmare Fuel\n|resultcount = 2\n|skill = Shadow Courtier\n|character = Wilson\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|item2 = Marsh Turf\n|item3 = Driftwood Piece\n|result = Dreaded Mudslinger\n|character = Wurt\n|skill = Terra Corruption\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|item2 = Mourning Glory\n|count2 = 3\n|result = Cursed Vexation\n|character = Wendy\n|skill = Shadow Sisterhood II\n}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Pure Horror\n|item2 = Rocks\n|tool = Shadowcraft Plinth\n|result = Pure Horror Rounds\n|resultcount = 20\n|character = Walter\n|skill = Shadow Slinger\n}}\n\n== {{pic|32|Placeholder}} Trivia ==\n* The opposite of this item is [[Pure Brilliance]].\n\n== {{Pic|32|Blueprint}} Gallery ==\n<gallery>\nPure Horror Droped.gif|Dropped Pure Horror.\nPure Horror Old.png|Beta Pure Horror Texture.\nPure Horror Droped Old.gif|Beta Dropped Pure Horror Texture.\n</gallery>\n<tabber>\nResources=\n{{Resources}}\n|-|\nCraftable Items=\n{{Craftable Items and Structures on DST}}\n</tabber>\n[[zh:绾补鎭愭儳]]\n[[vi:Pure Horror]]"
